m;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Xôi gấc đậu xanh</span></li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0.6em; margin-left: 1.3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Cháo trắng</span></li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0.6em; margin-left: 1.3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Bánh chưng / Bánh tét chay</span></li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0.6em; margin-left: 1.3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Chả lụa chay</span></li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0.6em; margin-left: 1.3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Mâm cơm chay (3 mặn, 1 xào, 1 canh, 1 cơm)</span></li></ul><h3 style=\"width: 1050px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; text-rendering: optimizespeed; font-family: &quot;Roboto Slab&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(254, 130, 78) !important; font-size: 16px !important; font-weight: 600 !important;\"><span id=\"Mam_cung_ram_mung_1_man\" style=\"-webkit-box-decoration-break: clone;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Mâm cúng rằm mùng 1 mặn</span></span></h3><ul style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3em; font-family: &quot;Roboto Slab&quot;, sans-serif;\"><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0.6em; margin-left: 1.3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Trái cây</span></li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0.6em; margin-left: 1.3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Hoa cúc kim cương</span></li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0.6em; margin-left: 1.3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Nhang rồng phượng</span></li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0.6em; margin-left: 1.3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Đèn cầy</span></li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0.6em; margin-left: 1.3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Gạo</span></li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0.6em; margin-left: 1.3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Muối</span></li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0.6em; margin-left: 1.3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Trà</span></li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0.6em; margin-left: 1.3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Rượu</span></li><